# Code ownership for review enforcement.
# Pair with branch protection on main to require review on the files
# that drive the release pipeline. The bot accounts that auto-bump
# version.txt are exempt via `Allow specified actors to bypass required
# pull requests` in the branch protection rule.

# Anything in this repo defaults to the maintainer.
*                               @igorjs

# Security-sensitive: the workflow definitions, build script, version
# pins, and upstream checksum manifest. Bot-generated PRs touching
# these need explicit human approval unless bypass is configured.
/.github/workflows/             @igorjs
/.github/CODEOWNERS             @igorjs
/build.sh                       @igorjs
/version.txt                    @igorjs
/libkrunfw-version.txt          @igorjs
/upstream-checksums.txt         @igorjs
